<%= content_for :thetitle do -%>Tidy-up your blog<%- end -%>

<p>I try to keep you blog tidy and neat, but sometimes you just need to go in and tidy up a bit.</p>

<ul class="thumbnails">
  <li class="span3">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <img src="/images/admin/delete-all-the-posts.jpg" />
      <div class="caption">
        <h5>Delete every post</h5>
        <p>This will delete every blog post in your Artigo blog. Use with caution.</p>
        <p><a href="#confirm_delete" data-toggle="modal" class="btn btn-danger">Nuke 'Em</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </li>
</ul>

<div class="modal fade hide" id="confirm_delete" style="display: none;">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <a class="close" data-dismiss="modal">Ã—</a>
    <h3>Really delete all the posts?</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <p>Every post in your blog will be deleted <strong>permanently</strong>. Are you sure you want to do this?</p>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <%= form_tag "/admin/tidyup/tidyposts" do -%>
      <input type="hidden" name="post_type" value="all" />
      <input type="submit" value="Yes, drop the bomb!" class="btn btn-danger" />
    <% end -%>
    <a href="#" class="btn" data-dismiss="modal">No, cancel</a>
  </div>
</div>
<br />
<hr />
